docs {
  # Update Item
  
  Update an item in a shopping list.
  
  ## Path Parameters
  
  - `familyId`: ID of the family
  - `listId`: ID of the shopping list
  - `itemId`: ID of the item
  
  ## Request Body
  
  - `name` (string, optional): Updated name for the item (1-200 characters)
  - `checked` (boolean, optional): Mark item as purchased (true) or not purchased (false)
  
  ## Response
  
  Returns the updated shopping list with the modified item.
  
  ## Status Codes
  
  - `200`: Item updated successfully
  - `400`: Validation error
  - `401`: Unauthorized (missing or invalid token)
  - `403`: Forbidden (not a family member)
  - `404`: Item or shopping list not found
}
